result.title: Codigo Mistreo v3.0
result.content:
Tecnoesis'16( Techno-Management festival of National Institute of Technology, Silchar), in association with HackerEarth presents you the 3rd version of the Codigo Mistreo.

Contest duration is 5 hrs. There will be 7-8 ACM — ICPC style algorithmic questions.

Contest Link Register Here

Date : 06/11/2016 Time : 9:00 PM IST

Problem Setter : Sourav Kr Paul(spaul100), Subham Gupta(grovyle)

PRIZES

Prizes Worth 10,000/- to be won!

For All India

Rank 1 : 4,000/- Amazon Gift Card **** Rank 2 : 2,000/- Amazon Gift Card **** Rank 3 : 1,000/- Amazon Gift Card

For NIT Silchar

Rank 1 : 1,500/-

Rank 2 : 1,000/-

Rank 3 : 500/-

Though this contest is open for all, prizes are only for participants from India.

Everyone need to fill this form to be eligible for prizes.

Note : You will be able to buy anything from the gift card without paying anything up to the amount in the card.

Please refrain from plagiarism.
